1 Adyaiva dutaḥ asmākam paścāt sthitaḥ āsīt,
2 Dutaḥ yaḥ naḥ ṣaṣṭhe paridhāvane pravṛttavān,
3 Mama mukhataḥ ekaṃ āghātaṃ mārjitaḥ;

7 Aham ca anyebhyaḥ sthānebhyaḥ laghutaraḥ
8 Agaccham, yathā alakshayena prayatnena
9 Ūrdhvam anugaccham āsurān vegavān;

10 Yada eva Virgiliḥ ārabhata: "Snehaḥ,
11 Guṇena prajvalitaḥ, sadā anyam prajvalayati,
12 Yāvat tasya jvālā bahiḥ prakāśate;

49 Evaṃ jānīhi yad doṣaḥ pratipakṣeṇa
50 ekaṃ pāpaṃ nindati,
51 sahaitena saha atra tasya haritā śuṣyati;

70 Yathā tvam abravīḥ: ‘Yugaṃ punar āvartate;
71 Nyāyo manuṣyāṇāṃ prathamo bhūyaḥ pravartate,
72 Nūtanā ca prajā divyāvatīrṇā bhavati’.

76 Yaḥ samastaḥ jagatīgataḥ āsīt
77 satyavati viśvāsenā, vikīrṇā
78 nityarājyapradūtāiḥ;

79 tava ca vacanaṃ sarvataḥ spṛṣṭam
80 anurūpam āsīt navaiḥ pravacanakaṛtṛbhiḥ;
81 ata eva aham tāṃsandeṣṭum pravṛttaḥ.

82 Tataḥ te mayi tāvad ārādhyāḥ prādṛśyanta,
83 yadā Domitiānena te paripīḍitāḥ āsann,
84 tadā mayāpi tatraiva sthitena tेषāṃ ruditam vinā na ruditam āsīt;

88 Tathā ca yāvat na aham Gṛkān nayāmi Tebe-nadyau
89 kāvyena, tāvat aham snāpitaḥ;
90 tataḥ paścāt bhayāt aham gūḍhaḥ ca āsam,

91 dīrghakālam pākhaṇḍam darśayan;
92 ayam ca mādhuryam mām caturtham maṇḍalam
93 caturthe śatatamaparicakramaṇam akārayat.

103 prathame valaye andhasya kārāgṛhasya;
104 bahuśaḥ vayam kathām kurmaḥ parvatasya
105 yaḥ sadā dhātrīḥ asmākaṃ sārdhaṃ asti."

112 Paśyasi tām yā Laṅghyāṃ prādarśayat;
113 Asti tatra Tiresiyasya duhita, Tētiśca,
114 Tasyāḥ saha bhaginībhiḥ Dēidamiyā.

115 Ubhau kavitau tataḥ tumautau
116 punar api dṛṣṭiṃ cakṣuṣoḥ paritaḥ prayojayitum
117 ārohaṇāt prapātāt ca vimuktāv abhūtām;

130 Api tu kṣipram madhurāṇi vākyāni bhagnavan,
131 Vṛkṣaḥ kaścid yam madhye mārgasya prāpamahe,
132 Sukumāra-gandha-yuktaiḥ svādiṣṭaiḥ phalaiḥ saha;

139 Ubhau kavitau vṛkṣam abhyupagacchataḥ;
140 śabdaś ca madhye patratālam
141 akarodīt: "Etad annam priyam bhaviṣyati."

151 Madhu ca śalabhāśca āhāraḥ
152 Ye bāptistam aranye poṣayām āsuḥ;
153 Tasmāt sa garīyān mahān ca asti,
